      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="1892_AS_RBH_1_00037"/>Hrn Dr. Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb730" type="place">III. Seidlgasse 30</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1892_AS_RBH_1_00038"/><salute>Lieber Richard,</salute></p><table><row><cell><rs ref="#pmb11485" type="person">P. G.</rs>:</cell><cell><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb40415" type="place">Paris, 51, rue Vivienne</rs>,</hi></cell></row><row><cell/><cell><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb29442" type="org">gazette de Francfort</rs>.</hi></cell></row></table><p>Ob ich heute im Caffé wei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s ich nicht; hoffentlich aber<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen wir uns <hi rend="underline" n="1"><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr</hi> bald.</p><closer>Herzlich Ihr getreuer<signed>Arthur.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
